X-Repackaging-Reasoning:
  Upstream sources are repackaged to remove a file which contains a pdf but
  not the source to generate it:
    + docs/ContributorStatement.pdf
  .
  Repackaging is done via debian/repack.sh and can be replayed using "uscan -f"

